Follow: https://www.stephenwagner.com/2020/03/18/how-to-raspberry-pi-4-as-an-iscsi-san-iscsi-target/
From - "Let’s get started, here’s the instructions…"
To - "Connect the ESXi Initiator"

Then use: https://www.informaticar.net/ubuntu-20-04-how-to-setup-iscsi-initiator/
To setup iSCSI initiator on client to connect to target. 
keep in mind that:
- On Client: /etc/iscsi/initiator.. 
        file name has to be the same as what is mapped in stephenwagners guide. i.e iqn.1991-05.com.microsoft:your.iscsi.initiator.iqn.com

